item.title: Jake and the Neverland Fruit Thieves game
item.description: Pirate Hook and his assistant decided to steal fruits from the island. But Jack and his parrot friend stand guard. The guy will observe the situation through a spyglass. As soon as Jake notices the pirates, immediately press the spacebar, then they will drop their burden, and the bird will take it. Show instant reaction to complete this task and save the island from another robbery by Hook.
